# Cloudflare type generation gate

Whenever an agent changes `wrangler.jsonc` or any `.dev.vars` file, it must regenerate Cloudflare binding types **before ending the task**.

## Required command (run from repo root)

```bash
pnpm run cf-typegen
```

## Expectations

- Do not skip type generation after changing `wrangler.jsonc` or `.dev.vars`.
- If `cf-typegen` modifies files, include those changes and ensure the repo still builds/tests as expected.
